constraint.SQL:
["tIB_XMXX.XMLX={0} 
and tIB_XMXX.ID in (
select t1.XMMC 
from lcIB_NHSP t1 
where t1.instid in (select id from jgcrm.os_wfentry t2 where t2.state=4)
and t1.hyjg=0 
)",[{"expression":"XMLX","scale":0,"length":0,"type":1}]]

["tIB_XMXX.XMLX={0} 
and tIB_XMXX.ID in (
select t1.XMMC 
from lcIB_NHSP t1 
where t1.instid in (select id from jgcrm.os_wfentry t2 where t2.state=4) 
and t1.hyjg=0 
) 
and tIB_XMXX.SSBM in (
SELECT t3.id FROM jgcrm.Lborganization t3
where 1=1 
start with t3.id ={1} connect by prior t3.id = t3.fid
)",[{"expression":"XMLX2","scale":0,"length":0,"type":1},{"expression":"$Login.User.OrgID","scale":0,"length":0,"type":1}]]

column.name: YJFXSL2

column.name: XMYJZSR2
column.expression: <%@ livebos language='javascript' %> ABS_SQLVALUE("select (t1.YJCXSR+t1.YJBJSR) from ecif.lcIB_LXSP t1 where t1.XMMC=? and rownum = 1 order by instid desc",[XMMC2])

column.name: LXRQ2
column.expression: <%@ livebos language='javascript' %> ABS_SQLVALUE("select to_number(to_char(finish_date,'YYYYMMDD')) from jgcrm.os_historystep where entry_id = (select max(instid) from ECIF.lcIB_LXSP where XMMC= ?) ",[XMMC2]);
